TY  - JOUR
TI  - Equilibrium and Stability
AU  - Allingham, M. G.
AB  - [This paper presents a model of an economy in which the formation of equilibrium is completely explained by the independent optimizing behavior of individual agents, and thus reformulates the concept of equilibrium in a way which is essentially related to that of stability.]
