TY  - JOUR
TI  - Asymptotic Minimum-MSE Prediction in the Cobb-Douglas Model with a Multiplicative Disturbance Term
AU  - Aigner, Dennis J.
AB  - [A nonparametric framework for deriving the asymptotic MSE-optimal predictor for a multiplicative model is presented. The resulting predictor is compared to several known competitors in a limited Monte Carlo experiment.]
